+
+/**
+ * Compact snapshots section shown inside the repo dropdown.
+ *
+ * Fetches /snapshots?repo=<active> on mount and on `refreshSignal` bumps,
+ * then renders a small list. Clicking a row switches to that snapshot via
+ * the host's onSwitchRepo (snapshots are real registered repos named
+ * `<repoName>@<shortHash>`). The trash icon deletes the snapshot.
+ *
